<main>
  <h1>A Memory to Keep Forever 💖</h1>

  <p>It was midnight, June 3rd, 2024. I was tired AF and just wanted to check in on you.
    I honestly have no clue what we talked about — I was half-asleep —  
    but I will never forget the last minute of that call.<br><br>

    Those three magic words:<br>  
    <strong>“I love you.”</strong><br><br>

    I literally woke up immediately. Like, shot up. Eyes wide. Fully alert.  
    After I said I felt the same way and we hung up, I just stared out my window  
    for a solid 10 legal minutes trying to process what had just happened.<br>

    You — a 100/10 man — really said it first.  
    Me?? A 5/10 woman living off anxiety and vibes??  
    Impossible.  
    ...At least I *thought* it was.
    Guess that makes us once in a lifetime. 💖
  </p>

